title: Our First Date
description: Coffee turned into a 5-hour conversation. I knew you were special from that very first laugh.

title: First Valentine's Day
description: You made me a handmade card that I still keep in my wallet. It was perfect, just like you.

title: Weekend Getaway
description: Our first trip together to the coast. We watched the sunset and I realized I wanted to see every sunset with you.

title: Adventure Together
description: We got lost on that hiking trail but found something better - complete trust in each other.

title: Summer Festival
description: Dancing with you under the fireworks, everything felt magical. That's when I knew I was falling hard.

title: First 'I Love You'
description: Watching the sunrise together, the words just came naturally. Your smile in that moment is burned into my memory forever.
